===Etymology===
Via {{etyl|enm}}, from {{etyl|fro}} ''[[heure]]'', from {{etyl|la}} {{term|hora|hōra|lang=la|hour}}, from
{{etyl|grc}} '''[[ὥρα]]''' (''hora'') "any time or period, whether of the year, month, or day".

